        * ace/ARGV.{h,cpp,inl}:
          Refactored ACE_ARGV to ACE_ARGV_T which is a template, where ACE_ARGV is
          now a typedef of ACE_ARGV_T<ACE_TCHAR>. Taken the idea from the wchar
          work of David Giovannini <giovannd at ociweb dot com>

