        * m4/config_h.m4:

          Changed ACE_LACKS_STRPTIME and ACE_LACKS_STRPTIME_PROTOTYPE
          feature tests to use the same idiom as similar tests.  This
          Avoids requiring an AH_TEMPLATE for each feature test macro
          in config_h.m4.

